page: blog
title: Blog homepage
keywords: web development, front end, developer, web developer, website portfolio, blog
slug: blog
layout: default.hbs
description: Alex Clapperton's Blog &mdash; Manchester, UK based front-end developer
changefreq: monthly
priority: 1.0
